<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hadmar V. von Laber, Pfleger zu Hemau, und Johann von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Pfalz-Neumarkt</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Rückgabe der zu Hemau beschlagnahmten Waren von Stefan Koler, Konrad Imhoff, Michael Imhoff, Heinrich Topler, Peter d. J. Mendel, Konrad Gruber, Sebald Imhoff, Georg Tetzel und Sebald Groland, Bürger zu Nürnberg, und kündigt Burkhard Reichertshofer, Diener der Stadt, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_409" id="203v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_409_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hadman von Laber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l2">Pfleger cʒu hembawr </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_409_r1l3">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> die <expan>hernachgeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l4">vvie Jn 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu hembawr etvvıeuil habe vnd <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l5">Mıchel Jm hof der <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> im Achten Jar <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l6">etvvieuil habe vnd <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> . herfüren vnd bringen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l7">ſülle / den Jr mitſampt <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habe cʒu hembawr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l8">aufgehalten habt / mitnamen dem Steffan Coler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l9">v pellein / <expan>Cuncʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Jmhof iij pellein <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Michel Jmhof </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l10">ij pellein . dem <expan>h<ex>einrich</ex></expan> . Topler iiij pellein . dem Peter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l11">Mendel dem <expan>Jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ij pellein / dem <expan cert="unknown">C</expan> . Gruber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l12">iij pellein . dem Sebolten Jmhof j pellein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l13">dem Jörg Tecʒell . j . pellein vnd dem <expan>Seb<ex>olt</ex></expan> Groland </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l14">
<del rend="strikethrough"> Grabner </del> . J . pellein / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Darümb ſenden vvir </del> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l15"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgern</ex></expan> . dy <expan>egeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> Jr habe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l16">vnd kauffmanſchaft / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ledig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l17">vnd on hindernüſſe volgen laſſen wöllet 
<del rend="strikethrough">Als etc </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l18">
<del rend="strikethrough">das wöllen etc </del> vnd waʒ auch <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Reykerſhof </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l22"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> B </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_409_r1l19">dyener </ab></add> . darümb cʒu diſem mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gnad </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_409_line_1571657302315_444">edell </ab></add> werb
<del rend="strikethrough">end ſey </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l23">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen . des wöllet Jm <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l24">darumb gütlich von euch vertigen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_409_line_1571657392269_460">Als etc </ab></add> . Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_409_r1l25">hercʒog <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex></expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_409" id="203v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hadman von Laber, pfleger czu Hembawr</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> die
                            <expan>hernachges<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie in Michel Imhof, der
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> im achten jar
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ist, etwievil habe und
                                <expan>kauffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan> herfüren und bringen sülle,
                        den ir mitsampt <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habe czu Hembawr
                        aufgehalten habt, mit namen dem Steffan Coler v pellein,
                                <expan>Cuncze<ex>n</ex></expan> Imhof iii pellein,
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Michel Imhof ii pellein, dem
                                <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Topler iiii pellein, dem Peter
                        Mendel dem <expan>jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ii pellein, dem <expan cert="unknown">C<ex>huncz</ex></expan> Gruber iii pellein, dem Sebolten
                        Imhof i pellein, dem Jörg Teczell i pellein und dem
                            <expan>Seb<ex>olt</ex></expan> Groland i pellein.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> dy <expan>eges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> ir
                        habe und kauffmanschaft durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ledig
                        und on hindernüsse volgen lassen wöllet; und waz auch
                                <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Reykershof,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>dyener</add>, darümb czu disem mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add>edell</add> werb von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, des wöllet
                        im <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und in darumb gütlich von euch vertigen.
                            <add>Als etc.</add> Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
